  "tells": [
    "Prioritize enabling Ugin's Labyrinth on turn 1 alongside Devourer of Destiny to manipulate the top cards and accelerate mana.",
    "Use Mystic Forge early to bypass mana constraints and play spells directly from the library.",
    "Deploy Kozilek's Command to develop the game plan and handle critical moments.",
    "Avoid playing Chalice of the Void or Talismans on turn 1 if playing first against an unknown opponent, as they may cost the game.",
    "Common mistakes include overextending into sweepers, forgetting to fetch basics for Tron, mismanaging Kozilek's Command (exiling the wrong thing), and not using Thought-Knot Seer early enough."
  ],
